itunes:subtitle: Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway are joined by former Miami Dolphins O-Lineman Jason Fox to talk about his new social music app with Patrick Mahomes and Baker Mayfield called EarBuds and how they came up with it — plus Jason’s weirdest Tim Tebow story fro...
itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway are joined by former Miami Dolphins O-Lineman Jason Fox to talk about his new social music app with Patrick Mahomes and Baker Mayfield called EarBuds and how they came up with it — plus Jason’s weirdest Tim Tebow story from college and Super Bowl pick, some casual Taylor Swift conversation, and Jason explains how foul football locker rooms really get by the end of the year.
